des:
Orange Smart Home products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on or turn off your light and plug.
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your light and plug - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.
After connecting Alexa to your Orange Smart Home products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Orange Smart Home" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register an account in our "Orange Smart Home" app;
(3). You need to have some Orange Smart Home devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "Orange Smart Home" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Orange Smart Home" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Orange Smart Home" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Orange Smart Home", and you'll be navigated to "Orange Smart Home" login page;
(9). Input your Orange Smart Home account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
Alexa, turn on the light.
Alexa, turn on the plug.
